content.title: Sit Down Startup Podcast
content.carrousel_body: There's a new podcast in town! Founders, CEOs, and makers chat with leaders about their startup journeys. There’s rule-flipping, new dogma, and recycling failure into growth. Plus, why customer experience is at the heart of success, as told by people who know unpredictability inside out.

content.title: Startup CX Awards
content.carrousel_body: Every year, we highlight the best and brightest at the Startup CX Awards. Out of many nominations, our judges selected four winners across four categories: Apps & Integrations, Seamless CX, Innovation and Data & Insights. Watch the event on-demand to get a behind-the-scenes look at CX from our four winners.

content.hero_body:
ZENDESK FOR EDUCATION

Show up for students and staff

Education is rapidly evolving and schools worldwide need to adapt to today’s digital climate. Providing students with the best education comes first, but budget cuts and rising expectations are a lot to balance at once. At Zendesk, we provide schools—big and small—with the right solution to support students, parents, and faculty under any circumstance.
